  "task_html": "\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0G7ryQXRNjQ&t=278s\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"video-link-card\">\n  <div class=\"video-link-icon\">▶</div>\n  <div class=\"video-link-text\">\n    <div class=\"video-link-title\">Erklärvideo ansehen</div>\n    <div class=\"video-link-sub\">YouTube: Fläche eines Kreisrings berechnen – einfach erklärt</div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"video-link-arrow\">↗</div>\n</a>\n\n<p>Berechne die fehlenden Größen für jeden Kreisring.</p>\n\n<div class=\"ring-grid\">\n\n  <!-- i): r_i und r_a gegeben → alles berechnen -->\n  <div class=\"ring-card\">\n    <div class=\"ring-card-label\" style=\"color:#2563eb\">i)</div>\n<svg viewBox=\"0 0 140 140\" class=\"ring-svg\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n      <circle cx=\"70\" cy=\"70\" r=\"60\" fill=\"#bfdbfe\" stroke=\"#2563eb\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"/>\n      <circle cx=\"70\" cy=\"70\" r=\"36\" fill=\"white\" stroke=\"#2563eb\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n      <circle cx=\"70\" cy=\"70\" r=\"2.5\" fill=\"#2563eb\"/>\n    </svg>\n    <div class=\"ring-data\">\n      <span class=\"ring-val inner\">r<sub>i</sub> = 3 cm</span>\n      <span class=\"ring-val outer\">r<sub>a</sub> = 5 cm</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"ring-inputs\">\n      <label>A<sub>innen</sub> =<input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"28.27\" placeholder=\"? cm²\"></label>\n      <label>A<sub>außen</sub> =<input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"78.54\" placeholder=\"? cm²\"></label>\n      <label>A<sub>Ring</sub> =<input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"50.27\" placeholder=\"? cm²\"></label>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- ii): A_innen und A_außen gegeben → A_ring berechnen -->\n  <div class=\"ring-card\">\n    <div class=\"ring-card-label\" style=\"color:#16a34a\">ii)</div>\n<svg viewBox=\"0 0 140 140\" class=\"ring-svg\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n      <circle cx=\"70\" cy=\"70\" r=\"60\" fill=\"#bbf7d0\" stroke=\"#16a34a\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"/>\n      <circle cx=\"70\" cy=\"70\" r=\"32\" fill=\"white\" stroke=\"#16a34a\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n      <circle cx=\"70\" cy=\"70\" r=\"2.5\" fill=\"#16a34a\"/>\n    </svg>\n    <div class=\"ring-data\">\n      <span class=\"ring-val\" style=\"background:#f0fdf4;color:#166534;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;padding:5px 10px;border-radius:6px;text-align:center;\">A<sub>innen</sub> = 19,63 cm²</span>\n      <span class=\"ring-val\" style=\"background:#dcfce7;color:#166534;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;padding:5px 10px;border-radius:6px;text-align:center;\">A<sub>außen</sub> = 66,48 cm²</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"ring-inputs\">\n      <label>A<sub>Ring</sub> =<input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"46.85\" placeholder=\"? cm²\"></label>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- iii): A_innen und d_a gegeben → A_außen und A_ring berechnen -->\n  <div class=\"ring-card\">\n    <div class=\"ring-card-label\" style=\"color:#d97706\">iii)</div>\n<svg viewBox=\"0 0 140 140\" class=\"ring-svg\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n      <circle cx=\"70\" cy=\"70\" r=\"60\" fill=\"#fde68a\" stroke=\"#d97706\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"/>\n      <circle cx=\"70\" cy=\"70\" r=\"25\" fill=\"white\" stroke=\"#d97706\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n      <circle cx=\"70\" cy=\"70\" r=\"2.5\" fill=\"#d97706\"/>\n    </svg>\n    <div class=\"ring-data\">\n      <span class=\"ring-val\" style=\"background:#fef9c3;color:#854d0e;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;padding:5px 10px;border-radius:6px;text-align:center;\">A<sub>innen</sub> = 12,57 cm²</span>\n      <span class=\"ring-val\" style=\"background:#fef08a;color:#854d0e;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;padding:5px 10px;border-radius:6px;text-align:center;\">d<sub>a</sub> = 9,6 cm</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"ring-inputs\">\n      <label>A<sub>außen</sub> =<input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"72.38\" placeholder=\"? cm²\"></label>\n      <label>A<sub>Ring</sub> =<input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"59.81\" placeholder=\"? cm²\"></label>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- iv): A_ring und r_a gegeben → r_i gesucht -->\n  <div class=\"ring-card\">\n    <div class=\"ring-card-label\" style=\"color:#9333ea\">iv) <span style=\"font-size:11px;font-weight:400\">r<sub>i</sub> gesucht</span></div>\n<svg viewBox=\"0 0 140 140\" class=\"ring-svg\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n      <circle cx=\"70\" cy=\"70\" r=\"60\" fill=\"#f0abfc\" stroke=\"#9333ea\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"/>\n      <circle cx=\"70\" cy=\"70\" r=\"42\" fill=\"white\" stroke=\"#9333ea\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n      <circle cx=\"70\" cy=\"70\" r=\"2.5\" fill=\"#9333ea\"/>\n    </svg>\n    <div class=\"ring-data\">\n      <span class=\"ring-val outer\" style=\"background:#faf5ff;color:#7e22ce;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;padding:5px 10px;border-radius:6px;text-align:center;\">r<sub>a</sub> = 4,4 cm</span>\n      <span class=\"ring-val\" style=\"background:#ede9fe;color:#7e22ce;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;padding:5px 10px;border-radius:6px;text-align:center;\">A<sub>Ring</sub> = 30,63 cm²</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"ring-inputs\">\n      <label>A<sub>außen</sub> =<input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"60.82\" placeholder=\"? cm²\"></label>\n      <label>A<sub>innen</sub> =<input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"30.19\" placeholder=\"? cm²\"></label>\n      <label>r<sub>i</sub> =<input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"3.1\" placeholder=\"? cm\"></label>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"check-bar\">\n  <button class=\"btn-check\" onclick=\"checkRing()\">✓ Überprüfen</button>\n  <button class=\"btn-reset\" onclick=\"resetRing()\">↺ Zurücksetzen</button>\n  <span class=\"check-result\" id=\"check-result-ring\"></span>\n</div>\n\n<style>\n.ring-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:14px;margin-top:16px;}\n.ring-card{background:#fafaf9;border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;padding:16px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:10px;}\n.ring-card-label{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:800;align-self:flex-start;}\n.ring-svg{width:130px;height:130px;}\n.ring-data{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:5px;width:100%;}\n.ring-val{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;padding:5px 10px;border-radius:6px;text-align:center;}\n.ring-val.inner{background:#f1f5f9;color:#334155;}\n.ring-val.outer{background:#e0f2fe;color:#0c4a6e;}\n.ring-inputs{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px;width:100%;}\n.ring-inputs label{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;color:var(--ink2);}\n.ring-inputs .cell-input{flex:1;min-width:0;text-align:right;}\n</style>\n",
  "sol_html": "\n<div class=\"ring-grid\">\n  <div class=\"ring-card\">\n    <div class=\"ring-card-label\" style=\"color:#2563eb\">i)</div>\n    <div style=\"font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;line-height:2;width:100%;\">\n      A<sub>i</sub> = π·3² ≈ <strong>28,27 cm²</strong><br>\n      A<sub>a</sub> = π·5² ≈ <strong>78,54 cm²</strong><br>\n      A<sub>Ring</sub> = 78,54−28,27 ≈ <strong>50,27 cm²</strong>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"ring-card\">\n    <div class=\"ring-card-label\" style=\"color:#16a34a\">ii)</div>\n    <div style=\"font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;line-height:2;width:100%;\">\n      A<sub>i</sub> = π·2,5² ≈ <strong>19,63 cm²</strong><br>\n      A<sub>a</sub> = π·4,6² ≈ <strong>66,48 cm²</strong><br>\n      A<sub>Ring</sub> ≈ <strong>46,85 cm²</strong>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"ring-card\">\n    <div class=\"ring-card-label\" style=\"color:#d97706\">iii)</div>\n    <div style=\"font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;line-height:2;width:100%;\">\n      r<sub>i</sub>=2 cm, r<sub>a</sub>=4,8 cm<br>\n      A<sub>i</sub> = π·4 ≈ <strong>12,57 cm²</strong><br>\n      A<sub>a</sub> = π·23,04 ≈ <strong>72,38 cm²</strong><br>\n      A<sub>Ring</sub> ≈ <strong>59,81 cm²</strong>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"ring-card\">\n    <div class=\"ring-card-label\" style=\"color:#9333ea\">iv)</div>\n    <div style=\"font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;line-height:2;width:100%;\">\n      A<sub>a</sub> = π·4,4² ≈ <strong>60,82 cm²</strong><br>\n      A<sub>i</sub> = 60,82−30,63 ≈ <strong>30,19 cm²</strong><br>\n      r<sub>i</sub> = √(30,19÷π) ≈ <strong>3,1 cm</strong>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n"
}